	depends on SWUPDATE_CONFIG_HAVE_FREEBSD
	default SWUPDATE_DEFAULT_SOCKET_NOTIFIER_DIRECTORY
	help
	  Path to SWUpdate's Notifier sockets on FreeBSD as
	  Linux-like abstract sockets are not available.

endmenu

